title: Do You Have Control Issues?
itunes:title: Do You Have Control Issues?
description:
Episode 633 - I believe we all have control issues in some sort of way. Either we always want to be in control or we feel like we are not in control of anything in our lives. In this episode, I am going to teach you the happy medium between the two. Follow me on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
